import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { Button, Row, Col, ListGroup, Image, Card, ListGroupItem, } from "react-bootstrap"; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; import { useDispatch, useSelector } from "react-redux"; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import Message from "../Components/Message"; import Loader from "../Components/Loader" import { orderDetails } from "../actions/orderActions"; const PlaceOrderScreen = () => { const dispatch = useDispatch(); const orderDetails = useSelector((state) => state.orderDetails); const { order, loading, error } = orderDetails; useEffect(() => { dispatch(orderDetails(order._id)) }, [dispatch, order]); return loading ? : error ? {error} : <>

Shipping

Address: {order.shippingAddress.address} , {order.shippingAddress.city}{" "} {order.shippingAddress.postalCode} ,{" "} {order.shippingAddress.country}

Method: {order.paymentMethod}

{order.orderItems.length === 0 ? ( Cart is Empty ) : ( {order.orderItems.map((item, index) => ( {item.name} {item.qty} X ${item.price} = $ {(item.qty * item.price).toFixed(2)} ))} )}

Order Summary
